{"Id":699015,"Title":"浪淘沙令 四景乐道辞","Dynasty":"明","Author":"程敏政","Context":"春雨夜如何。花靥红多。窗前黄鸟数声过。斜挂氅衣初睡起，日上庭柯。人世苦奔波。两鬓霜皤。争如溪上理渔蓑。笑问东风来几阵，酒满香螺。竹院好风凉。洗尽炎光。呼童閒试水沈香。数卷南华看未了，且困藤床。官道暗尘黄。四体流浆。可能知有翠寒堂。尽日茶瓜留客坐，一调沧浪。秋意到郊亭。水褪沙汀。金茎香泻瓮头青。柱杖西畴看稻了，细检丹经。蒲柳最先零。羲驭难停。旧时交友似晨星。惟有黄花开更好，多谢园丁。庭满冻苔斑。农事都閒。尖风不到水云间。曝背茅檐调鹤舞，一任疏顽。名利几人还。雪拥关山。金丹留我镜中颜。起索梅花同一笑，紧闭柴关。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"浪淘沙","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"75a0fbc915b45faec6eb4f56fa082cef","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6312796,"Sentence":"春雨夜如何。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chūn yǔ yè rú hé ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6312797,"Sentence":"花靥红多。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huā yè gōng duō ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6312798,"Sentence":"窗前黄鸟数声过。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chuāng qián huáng diǎo shǔ shēng guō ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6312799,"Sentence":"斜挂氅衣初睡起，日上庭柯。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xié guà chǎng yī chū shuì qi ，rì shǎng tǐng kē ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6312800,"Sentence":"人世苦奔波。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"rén shì kǔ bēn bō ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6312801,"Sentence":"两鬓霜皤。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"liǎng bìn shuāng pó ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6312802,"Sentence":"争如溪上理渔蓑。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhēng rú xī shǎng li yú suō ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6312803,"Sentence":"笑问东风来几阵，酒满香螺。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xiào wèn dōng fēng lái jī zhèn ，jiu mǎn xiāng luó ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6312804,"Sentence":"竹院好风凉。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhú yuàn hǎo fēng liáng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"So